      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Collagen synthesis</strong>
        <p>Essential cofactor for collagen production, which maintains the skin barrier (first line of immune defense), supports wound healing, and builds healthy bones, teeth, and connective tissue in growing children.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Iron absorption enhancer</strong>
        <p>Vitamin C increases non-heme iron absorption by 2-3x by converting ferric iron to the more bioavailable ferrous form. Critical for children at risk of iron deficiency, particularly picky eaters and vegetarians.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Antioxidant protection</strong>
        <p>Neutralizes free radicals generated during immune responses, protecting immune cells from self-inflicted oxidative damage and supporting the resolution of inflammation after infection.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

